- cs.HC (Human-Computer Interaction) is another possible category as the paper discusses the design of a hardware accelerator for efficient impostor detection in smartphones. 
- cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition) is a possible category as the paper deals with sensor data and the use of deep learning for classification. 
- cs.SY (Systems and Control) is also a possible category as the paper discusses the design of a hardware accelerator for efficient impostor detection.
